Class UnresolvedValue

java.lang.Object
  org.smartfrog.sfcore.languages.sf.sfcomponentdescription.UnresolvedValue

public class UnresolvedValue
extends java.lang.Object

Stores an unresolved value and the source of the unresolved value. This is used by ResolutionState to store unresolved values and their source

equals

public boolean equals(java.lang.Object o)
Cheks for equality. Two unresolved values are equal if their values are equal and both their sources are the same (null or equal). Equality does not include the cause of the non-resolution.
